</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="nav container">
    <i class='bx bx-menu' id="menu-icon"></i>
    <a href="/" class="logo">
      <div class="logo-container">
        <img src="/img/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="site-logo">
        <span class="logo-text">Globe<span class="auto-link">AutoLink</span></span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <ul class="navbar" id="navbar">
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/less3years">-3 Years</a></li>
      <li><a href="/recentlyadded">Recently added</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about"  class="active">About</a></li>
      {{#unless user}}
        <li><a href="/login">Login/Signup</a></li>
      {{else}}
       <li><a href="/favorites">favorites</a></li>
        <li class="dropdown">
    <a href="#" class="dropbtn" id="profileToggle">Profile <i class="fa fa-caret-down"></i></a>
    <ul class="dropdown-content" id="profileMenu">
      {{#if (eq user.role "admin")}}
        <li><a href="/admin/users">Admin</a></li>
      {{/if}}
      <li><a href="/profil">My Profile</a></li>
      <li>
         <form action="/auth/logout" method="POST">
          <button type="submit">Logout</button>
        </form>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
      {{/unless}}
    </ul>
     <div>
    {{!-- <button id="toggleDarkMode" class="lang" data-i18n="dark_mode"> Dark Mode </button> --}}
    <button id="toggleDarkMode" class="lang" aria-label="Toggle dark mode">
      <i class='bx bx-moon'></i>
    </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="about-hero">
  <h1>About GlobeAutoLink</h1>
  <h2>
    More than a Marketplace</p>
    </h2> We’re empowering Algerians to import their cars safely, transparently, and with full support <br> by guiding them through every step of the process.
  </p>
</section>
<br><br>
<section class="about-section container">
  <div class="about-card">
    <h3>Our Story</h3>
    <p>
      Born from frustration with Algeria's complex import regulations, GlobeAutoLink started as a mission: help citizens access vehicles legally and affordably.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-card">
    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>
      We combine digital innovation with real-world expertise to support Algerians from car search to customs clearance.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-card">
    <h3>What We Offer</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>✔️ Legal + Technical Consultations</li>
      <li>✔️ Step-by-step import guidance</li>
      <li>✔️ Smart car search tools</li>
      <li>✔️ Secure online process</li>
      <li>✔️ Support in every region</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="about-card">
    <h3>Our Vision</h3>
    <p>
      We want every Algerian citizen and everyone to have access to modern cars, safely, transparently, and with full support at every stage.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
<br>
<section class="how-to-use">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>How to Use Our Platform</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <h3>1. Create Your Account</h3>
        <p>Register for free and get access to your personal dashboard to start your import journey.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>2. Find Your Car</h3>
        <p>Use our intelligent search tools to find vehicles from verified international sources that comply with Algerian import regulations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>3.Choose a Consultation Package</h3>
        <p>Select a support package that fits your needs. Each package includes access to customs, legal, financial, and technical experts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>4. Upload Your Documents</h3>
        <p>Submit your required documents directly on the platform. Our consultants will review everything step by step.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>5. Track Progress & Get Support</h3>
        <p>Follow every step from approval to delivery with real-time updates and guidance from your assigned team of experts.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-gallery">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>What You Can Do with GlobeAutoLink</h2>
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/img/explore.png" alt="Explore cars">
        <p>Browse cars from trusted sources abroad</p>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/img/filtre.png" alt="Apply filters">
        <p>Use smart filters to refine your search</p>
      </div>
  </div>
</section>
<br><br>
<footer>
  <div class="footer-top">
